{
  "info": {
    "name": "IPO Aggregation API v3",
    "description": "IPO Aggregation Platform — scrape SEBI/BSE/NSE/SME, resolve PDFs into sections (R2-hosted), extract structured fields via Firecrawl or DeepSeek, validate, and ship via webhook to Next.js.\n\n## Base URLs\n- Local: `http://127.0.0.1:8001`\n- Production: set the `base_url` collection variable\n\n## Authentication\nMost reads are open. Write endpoints (`POST /api/refresh`, optionally others) check `INTERNAL_API_KEY` if set in the server env. When set, send it as either header:\n- `X-Internal-Key: <key>`\n- `Authorization: Bearer <key>`\n\nLeave it blank locally for open access.\n\n## Lifecycle\n1. **Scrape** → `POST /api/refresh` — fetches all sources, diffs against DB.\n2. **Resolve** → `POST /api/ipos/{id}/resolve` — downloads PDFs, splits into sections, uploads each section's markdown to R2.\n3. **Parse** → `POST /api/ipos/{id}/parse-firecrawl` (preferred) or `/parse-sections` (DeepSeek) — extracts structured fields per section.\n4. **Validate + Unify** runs automatically inside parse → sets `publish_status` on `ipo_master`.\n5. **Read** → `GET /api/ipos/{id}/unified` — the single contract you ship to Next.js.\n\nLong ops return `{task_id}` immediately. Poll `GET /api/tasks/{task_id}` for progress.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "ipo-scraper-v3"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health & System",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health (liveness)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/health", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["health"] },
            "description": "Cheap liveness check — DB connection + config visibility. No external API calls."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Health (deep — probes R2/Firecrawl/DeepSeek)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/health?deep=true", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["health"], "query": [{ "key": "deep", "value": "true" }] },
            "description": "Probes every external dependency: list R2 bucket, GET Firecrawl /team, GET DeepSeek /models. Use during a deploy to verify all secrets are correct."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Dashboard Stats",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/dashboard/stats", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "dashboard", "stats"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Recent Scraper Logs",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/dashboard/logs?limit=10", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "dashboard", "logs"], "query": [{ "key": "limit", "value": "10" }] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Status Changes (audit)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/status-changes?limit=20", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "status-changes"], "query": [{ "key": "limit", "value": "20" }] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Scrape (background)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Trigger full scrape (returns task_id)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "X-Internal-Key", "value": "{{internal_api_key}}", "description": "Required only when INTERNAL_API_KEY is set on the server.", "disabled": false }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/refresh?year=2026", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "refresh"], "query": [{ "key": "year", "value": "2026" }] },
            "description": "Runs SEBI + BSE + NSE + SME concurrently. Skips IPOs already at `status=listed`. Returns task_id immediately — poll /api/tasks/{id} for progress."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Trigger scrape (no year filter)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "X-Internal-Key", "value": "{{internal_api_key}}", "disabled": false }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/refresh", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "refresh"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Background Tasks",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List recent tasks",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/tasks?limit=20", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "tasks"], "query": [{ "key": "limit", "value": "20" }] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Poll a task",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/tasks/abc123def456", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "tasks", "abc123def456"] },
            "description": "Replace abc123def456 with the task_id returned by /api/refresh, /api/ipos/{id}/resolve, or /parse-*. Status values: pending → running → completed | failed."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
